gw.api.domain.fundstracking

Class PaymentItemsNarrative

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.domain.fundstracking.PaymentItemsNarrative

  • public class PaymentItemsNarrative
extends java.lang.Object
    Tracks the PaymentItemActions the contexts in which they have occurred in the current bundle for use in creating PaymentItemGroup in the IFundsTracking plugin.
